## #[[Connectivity]]:
* [WaveLan](WiFi) - Extension that allows 802.11b [[WiFi]] cards [Download Demo](http://www.ff.iij4u.or.jp/~ngc/eng/newtwave.htm) _Registration Closed_
* *More [[WiFi]] Cards* - A [Paul Guyot](PaulGuyot) project that enables additional [[WiFi]] cards to work with the Newton (including my own Compaq WL110) [Download](http://www.kallisys.com/newton/morewifi/) _Freeware_
* [[EthernetDrivers]] - Need these for the [[WiFi]] drivers to work. Also used with my wired 3Com card
* [[Blunt]] - Bluetooth stack by [Eckhart Köppen](EckhartKoeppen), useful for moving files with [[BluetoothOBEX]] [Download](http://40hz.org/wiki/index.php/Blunt) _Freeware_
